Content.bodyText:
Darren,
This looks a like a really nice package and I love the fact I will be able to have total control of the PDF and layout, rather than just a HTML dump of the page into a PDF.

Does your doccumentation cover the xsl:fo stuff or is there somewhere else you can link to for in-depth documentation.

Warren
